Command : purge
Usage   : purge

This gives a manual way of purging all the user files so that the users who
have not logged in for a given period of time, and who have expire set to YES,
will have all theif files deleted.
A purge is automatically done when the talker is booted, and also everytime
the non-use period has expired after the boot.
CAUTION:  With a purge the system may be terporarily lagged.
